# CSS standards

- Mobile-first base styles; enhance with `min-width` media queries
- Design tokens in `:root` custom properties
- Fluid type: `clamp(min, preferred, max)` with `rem` in preferred
- Intrinsic grid: `repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(300px, 100%), 1fr))`
- Container queries when component context matters
- Support `prefers-color-scheme` and `prefers-reduced-motion`
- Relative units for spacing/type; plain CSS only — no preprocessors
- No inline styles in HTML
